{"tid":111082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"特首選舉民間全民投票","createTime":"2017-02-07T07:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T06:22:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bce8b710c03348d16ae7b36ed292a016da5295d3","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8-637967003054301%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=792d0541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/</a><br />\n<br />\n特首選舉民間全民投票<br />\n4 hrs &middot; <br />\n<br />\n邊個做特首？監察權在手！<br />\n<br />\n全民提名，抗衡篩選 <br />\n<br />\n「2017特首民投」民間提名開始<br />\n<br />\n提名網站：<br />\n<a href=\"https://cast.popvote.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcast.popvote.hk&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b64e8f3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cast.popvote.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n提名期：2月7日(10:00)至2月22日(17:00)<br />\n參選人：(共12人，系統在每次載入時隨機編排次序)<br />\n步驟一：雙重認証(身份証號碼+手機號碼)<br />\n步驟二：選擇提名其中一人為「2017特首民投」民間候選人<br />\n<br />\n往眾籌平台支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.do/supportcecr2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.do%2Fsupportcecr2017&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b399cc4d\" target=\"_blank\">bit.do/supportcecr2017</a>"},{"pid":"42337a9c091fb7579057189494d540e623e2e83c","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p235x350/16427250_652531708264497_6727531082557807904_n.jpg?oh=4e8918088f5ce8b2be8db7e894a2af4b&amp;oe=593D8ABB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp235x350%2F16427250_652531708264497_6727531082557807904_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4e8918088f5ce8b2be8db7e894a2af4b%26oe%3D593D8ABB&h=e50ad883&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a88e0990997cca9ef0c787bdf7b9342eb796111","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16473116_652202271630774_1193431775368191094_n.jpg?oh=8deea83303d9a27178ed1f6e7f34a829&amp;oe=593C133B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16473116_652202271630774_1193431775368191094_n.jpg%3Foh%3D8deea83303d9a27178ed1f6e7f34a829%26oe%3D593C133B&h=16d1832d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6020e0397da4b952d07d841ee4f62c488273eeb8","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱提名咗 曾俊華"},{"pid":"626a15ca7867e14d6994772dcd0acce9bd00c35d","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"Popvote 普及投票網站[url]<br />\n<a href=\"https://popvote.hk/cecr2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpopvote.hk%2Fcecr2017%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2fd3b313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://popvote.hk/cecr2017/</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"4e6c7b34b6fac8db8db964f82d24e9895f3d0380","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"Popvote 普及投票網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://popvote.hk/cecr2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpopvote.hk%2Fcecr2017%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2fd3b313\" target=\"_blank\">https://popvote.hk/cecr2017/</a>"},{"pid":"b6a3cf86bb0778613cc315de2ac81d8b8050dffd","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"民間提名階段:<br />\n<br />\n由2017年1 月16至31日期間，任何人士皆可向香港大學民意研究計劃郵寄「意向書」，表示有意成為「2017特首民投」候選人。所有完成參與民間提名的手續的民間候選人以及所有在2017年2 月4日下午五時前已公開宣布有意參選官方的2017特首選舉的人士，亦會自動成為「2017特首民投」參選人。 由2017年2 月7至22日期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">所有年滿18歲之香港市民可以透過手機網站程式或普及投票網頁，從各「2017特首民投」參選人中，提名其中一人。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></span> 任何「2017特首民投」參選人取得37,790 個或以上提名（按: 登記選民的總數是3,779,085，1% 就是37,790）將被視作成功得到民間提名，成為「2017特首民投」的民間候選人。"},{"pid":"e8d1cde166144ced08458e4dc2f864e6d62d5e19","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"公民聯合行動：2017特首選舉民間全民投票 Chief Executive Election Civil Referendum 2017<br />\n<a href=\"https://civicsq.com/t/2017-chief-executive-election-civil-referendum-2017/241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcivicsq.com%2Ft%2F2017-chief-executive-election-civil-referendum-2017%2F241&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e4866c77\" target=\"_blank\">https://civicsq.com/t/2017-chief-executive-election-civil-referendum-2017/241</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載facebook 解答：<br />\n<br />\n問：點解戴教授的fb文章說:「市民可經由手機程式、網頁或實體投票站...」？其實係唔係有機會三個途徑都全部支援？提供埋網頁投票的額外effort估唔係太多？況且又可以互為後備系統。<br />\n<br />\n答：是的. 市民可以經由 3 個途徑投票. 我們 3 個途徑都會支援. 但當然手機程式的方便和私隱度是最高的. 但市民可以自由選擇. 而且順帶一提, 在 622 已 install POPVOTE app 的市民, 只需在系統 ready 之後 update app 就可以使用, 無需重新安裝"},{"pid":"99985eda874c760fc08c87ff932116c6e304f811","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8-637967003054301%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=792d0541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/</a><br />\n<br />\n特首選舉民間全民投票<br />\n5 hrs &middot; <br />\n<br />\n2017特首選舉民間全民投票提名步驟<br />\n1. 登入官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://cast.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcast.popvote.hk%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=02f2264b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cast.popvote.hk/</a><br />\n2. 同意細則<br />\n3. 登記手提電話號碼<br />\n4. 輸入認證編號, 會以sms或致電傳送 (telegram用戶則會以telegram傳送)<br />\n5. 輸入名字作telegram開戶用途 (設有雙重認證的telegram用戶則須輸入密碼）<br />\n6. 輸入身份證號碼<br />\n7. 選擇心儀候選人在其名字下按提名<br />\n8. 完成<br />\n<br />\n有關如何確保私人資料不會洩露或被濫用, 詳見﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://civicsq.com/t/2017-17/340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcivicsq.com%2Ft%2F2017-17%2F340&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b17014a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://civicsq.com/t/2017-17/340</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝關注！<br />\n#特首民投 #civilreferendum<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n眾籌<br />\n整個「特首民投」計劃預算HK$1,500,000，請各位大力到眾籌平台集資支持~~<br />\nbit.do/supportcecr2017"},{"pid":"d16dbf89187f2b745a11f4ad819facdd883f1963","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8-637967003054301%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=792d0541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-637967003054301/</a><br />\n<br />\n特首選舉民間全民投票<br />\n5 hrs &middot; <br />\n<br />\n2017特首選舉民間全民投票提名步驟<br />\n1. 登入官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://cast.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcast.popvote.hk%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=02f2264b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cast.popvote.hk/</a><br />\n2. 同意細則<br />\n3. 登記手提電話號碼<br />\n4. 輸入認證編號, 會以sms或致電傳送 (telegram用戶則會以telegram傳送)<br />\n5. 輸入名字作telegram開戶用途 (設有雙重認證的telegram用戶則須輸入密碼）<br />\n6. 輸入身份證號碼<br />\n7. 選擇心儀候選人在其名字下按提名<br />\n8. 完成<br />\n<br />\n有關如何確保私人資料不會洩露或被濫用, 詳見﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://civicsq.com/t/2017-17/340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcivicsq.com%2Ft%2F2017-17%2F340&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b17014a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://civicsq.com/t/2017-17/340</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝關注！<br />\n#特首民投 #civilreferendum<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n眾籌<br />\n整個「特首民投」計劃預算HK$1,500,000，請各位大力到眾籌平台集資支持~~<br />\nbit.do/supportcecr2017</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16473313_652613081589693_7508834991979506187_n.jpg?oh=24cb07dcda33fe9aacecb3cfb8208cfe&amp;oe=593E101C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16473313_652613081589693_7508834991979506187_n.jpg%3Foh%3D24cb07dcda33fe9aacecb3cfb8208cfe%26oe%3D593E101C&h=9ea0f4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d1fc1a96ad6719073d2664e8088730e6d5c1b8d","tid":111082,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"投完咁又點？我真係有票投咩？"},{"pid":"6207f7d7ebd274ff67856875e3143d704135e2a0","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"提名期：2月7日(10:00)至2月22日(17:00)"},{"pid":"10661a9aa7e7d3c2c93f5b11fc0cf0e9968ecc44","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:02:29.000Z","msg":"提名期：2月7日(10:00)至2月22日(17:00)"},{"pid":"076ed315a25f69654a22f50dfa94e9609e3a85cb","tid":111082,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:28:27.000Z","msg":"順便收集公眾資料 身分證 電話號碼等"},{"pid":"6765791736e68d47c7060d84c72c05c41c4c0087","tid":111082,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:32:04.000Z","msg":"陳雲：長毛與曾俊華的方法一樣。曾俊華是用眾籌，累積百萬港元來脅迫民主派選委投票給他。長毛是用民間提名的方法，累積幾萬個民間提名來脅迫民主派選委投票給他。原來是連環騙局，前者騙取金錢，後者騙取選民投票數據和身份資料。<br />\n然而，泛民的支持者最容易騙，因為他們與曾俊華和長毛一樣，都是同樣地邪惡，自私自利，心術不正。泛民的支持者離地賣港，他們的故鄉在加拿大，對於他們，香港只是可以變賣的地方。曾俊華堅決支持二十三條立法，遲些長毛如果可以入閘，也會同樣支持，然後在條文細節上辯論。"},{"pid":"518846179b2cb7a0dc60affe481a229785a745b7","tid":111082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"特首選舉民間全民投票 （2017 特首民投）<br />\nPage Liked &middot; Yesterday &middot; <br />\n <br />\n我們的全版廣告，今日終於出街啦~<br />\n唔知有無人留意到呢?<br />\n<br />\n#2017特首民投<br />\nLikeShow more reactionsCommentShare<br />\nChronological<br />\n229 229<br />\n21 shares<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16425864_653098361541165_2761720359667467414_n.jpg?oh=01dbdef385ba93a1d4b3c5beac8562cb&amp;oe=5941DE49\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16425864_653098361541165_2761720359667467414_n.jpg%3Foh%3D01dbdef385ba93a1d4b3c5beac8562cb%26oe%3D5941DE49&h=3da53fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"602e938efd8b9beca73ee0968b4d909c471dfe05","tid":111082,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"五年前搞既話，689高票當選"},{"pid":"c49c7c452717e652015a258493152a0cc8d58fed","tid":111082,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五年前搞既話，689高票當選</blockquote><br />\n呢個係民意"},{"pid":"b38e1ff71c893d2d1b20397ec2a8d7d4bdd4e361","tid":111082,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB